This paper discusses the use of Hadoop-MapReduce in Cloud Computing, which falls under the category of Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC). The paper also focuses on scheduling improvements in Hadoop, which is related to Distributed Systems (cs.DS) and Computational Complexity (cs.CC). Additionally, the paper provides guidelines for improving scheduling in Hadoop, which is related to Software Engineering (cs.SE) and Systems and Control (cs.SY).
